STATE of North Carolina
v.
Shemar FROST No. 49P19 Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 4, 2019 Shemar Frost, for Frost, Shemar. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, Ernie Lee, District Attorney, for State of N.C.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 31st of January 2019 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Onslow County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 4th of February 2019."
